"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"We’ll use a VPN, Tor Browser, Njalla, and Zcash to buy a domain and get a website online without giving up any of your personal information 🙌.\\n\\n### Step 1. Create a Njalla Account\\n\\nNjalla is a “privacy-aware” domain registrar. Using a traditional domain registrar like GoDaddy to buy a domain like vandelayindustries.com would require that you provide your real name, billing address, credit card information, etc. It doesn’t help that when we give out our personal information [it always seems to get hacked](https://www.pcmag.com/news/godaddy-hacked-12m-customers-at-risk-of-phishing-attack). When you use Njalla, none of that applies. All you need is cryptocurrency.\\n\\nFirst, go to njallalafimoej5i4eg7vlnqjvmb6zhdh27qxcatdn647jtwwwui3nad.onion in Tor Browser and create an account. You can visit [Njalla’s public website](https://njal.la/) to confirm their onion address - just scroll to the bottom of the page to find it.\\n\\n![Njalla account signup screen](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Z3vxnrF4GZpOIqXeJLGBY.png?height=1794&width=2224)\\n\\n### Step 2: Add Funds\\n\\nGo to Account > Wallet > Add Funds\\n\\nNjalla allows you to pay using Zcash, a private cryptocurrency. A premium domain costs around $50 USD per year, so we’ll send that much to our Njalla Wallet. Wait for the transaction to complete before navigating away from this page.\\n\\n![Zcash payment QR code](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/55ODYEt8ERBt2S6uYkGDm.png?height=1794&width=2224)\\n\\n### Step 3: Buy a Domain\\n\\nClick on the Domains tab and search for a domain.\\n\\n![Domain Search](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Z3G2GynzQjQsMcptLg0H6.png?height=1794&width=2224)\\n\\nSelect and purchase the domain with the funds that you deposited. When you’ve completed registration you’ll see a success message.\\n\\n![Successfully purchased a domain](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/3rEJLtHFHBCmsJWOLz5xy.png?height=1794&width=2224)\\n\\n### Step 4: Create a Bitlaunch Account\\n\\nGo to [bitlaunch.io](https://bitlaunch.io/) and create a new account.\\n\\n![Bitlaunch homepage](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/NabvCduftGhL3_m1zlkiq.png?height=1794&width=2224)\\n\\n### Step 5: Add Funds\\n\\nBitlaunch allows you to pay with Bitcoin, Etherium, or Litecoin. Deposit as much as you’d like to get started.\\n\\n![BitLaunch etherium deposit QR code](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/uaZi43NzQkS0Y9qKfjT4-.png?height=1794&width=2224)\\n\\n### Step 6: Create a Server\\n\\nI chose BitLaunch with a Debian image.\\n\\n![Creating a new server on BitLaunch](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/2yf2uTjFaf2A7o7z_NUs9.png?height=897&width=1112)\\n\\n### Step 7: Install NGINX\\n\\n*This is the only step we’ll take outside of the Tor network so you should have a [trusted VPN](https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/reviews/best-vpn-service/) running.*\\n\\nWhen you created your server you also created an SSH login password. Log in to your server and [install NGINX](https://pimylifeup.com/raspberry-pi-nginx/).\\n\\n![Installing NGINX on the BitLaunch server.](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Z-lJSxm7Gg44dqsVlBgJX.png?height=966&width=1364)\\n\\n### Step 8: Update Your Domain’s DNS Settings\\n\\nBack at Njalla on the Domains tab click Manage next to your domain.\\n\\n![Domains tab at Njalla](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/6rQpMVNNBLztbVdQeuFgc.png?height=1794&width=2224)\\n\\nOn the DNS Settings tab, you’ll see the option to add a new DNS record. In the content field, enter the IP address of your BitLaunch server. Click the + button when you’re done.\\n\\n![Adding your servers IP address to the domain's DNS records](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/IkM0OFXR8u6Ld3ecGdShO.png?height=897&width=2224)\\n\\n### Step 9: Visit your new website\\n\\nEnter your domain name into your browser and visit your new website!\\n\\n![Default NGINX landing page on the new domain](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/G72cExvfQ0uACDMY3SpwV.png?height=1794&width=2224)\\n\\n🎉 Congratulations, you just kept your IP address, real name, credit card information, billing address, email address, device information, browser information, and browsing history private!\\n\\nQuestions? Follow me on Twitter [@glennsorrentino](https://twitter.com/glennsorrentino).\",\"timestamp\":1637908208,\"title\":\"🚀 Launch a public website without giving up your personal information\"},\"digest\":\"49vkfw16v-AE2lH-CXKn7N9NeCh-GPpMlzBgEVpI3L8\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xf4A3BBB8560D149C116d67CA5917A186cc13Fe30\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"vWlImahoGYV67vw7XX_VucRpo5RT47X35ofZ0thFCEs\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"rw6eBnmJo5znIw_IhL7GMo3KW4ULPM4BecOGXXtq2_c\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"i6ovlB1xNTEEg6TbZGzgeJ36m7QyX0p8UIvOhslD3rpEnXVY9DkN_oRno4gT2qDilF7XIL82BJxHK2k9GZPzLA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xebdc05550e7fcc4910ea495855552fb90e42e319474dac78eeabda8b839883d72249ec17e6a81fe9096b5ed26a6d828d52726f905d2d8df424f2846c454a63351c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"vWlImahoGYV67vw7XX_VucRpo5RT47X35ofZ0thFCEs\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"rw6eBnmJo5znIw_IhL7GMo3KW4ULPM4BecOGXXtq2_c\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"iastUUFjGm0zRLNbxNZvdQobjaOjE1wpGAVvB0fKSOA\"}"